# Context structure

This chapter explains how provided information will be structured:
1. Main task description - this part contains general information about task type, task target and required amount of times this task must be completed (task quantity).
2. Previous variant of plan and it's critique - this part contains a previously generated plan and it's critique.
3. Character state - this part contains detailed information about character state, including: weapon, armor, attributes, skills, inventory and etc.
4. Game world map - this part contains list of all resources, monsters and workshops on map with their coordinates.

